842
01:09:07,360 --> 01:09:09,351
Right, right, right. OK, fine.

843
01:09:10,360 --> 01:09:15,195
In <i>Derek,</i> this Rhode Island
Supreme Court, these same judges,

844
01:09:15,320 --> 01:09:20,155
said that, in a case
based on circumstantial theory,

845
01:09:20,280 --> 01:09:24,751
the case falls apart
if any part of the theory is weak.

846
01:09:25,880 --> 01:09:28,952
If there's a weak link,
then you throw the whole chain out?

847
01:09:29,080 --> 01:09:31,036
Exactly.

848
01:09:32,080 --> 01:09:34,878
Peter, that's good. That's very good.

849
01:09:39,160 --> 01:09:42,038
- Oh, yeah, this is good.
