Can I have a glass of water, please?

857
01:10:13,840 --> 01:10:18,152
No. The reason I'm here...
my affidavit is inaccurate.

858
01:10:22,160 --> 01:10:25,391
Great. Just what I need right now.

859
01:10:25,520 --> 01:10:27,795
- It's slow.
- Yeah.

860
01:10:27,920 --> 01:10:31,674
I left something out,
something incredibly important.

861
01:10:31,800 --> 01:10:35,759
Remember I gave Alex's drugs
to a woman at Clarendon Court?

862
01:10:35,880 --> 01:10:36,835
Yeah. So?

863
01:10:36,960 --> 01:10:39,599
That bitch was definitely
Sunny von Bulow.

864
01:10:42,400 --> 01:10:46,313
David... this is bad.

865
01:10:46,440 --> 01:10:50,319
It looks bad. I've met with you
five times now, and all of a sudden...

866
01:10:50,440 --> 01:10:52,556
No, it's not sudden.

867
01:10:52,680 --> 01:10:56,878
I think I always knew, but I became
convinced by staring at pictures of her.

868
01:10:59,960 --> 01:11:04,158
We can't use your affidavit unless
it's truthful. Are you sure this time?

869
01:11:04,280 --> 01:11:08,273
I swear... on the body
and soul of my mother.

870
01:11:09,280 --> 01:11:11,396
Poor woman.

871
01:11:13,520 --> 01:11:17,798
