895
01:13:08,840 --> 01:13:11,673
<i>I'd been offered a new position</i>
<i>in the oil business,</i>

896
01:13:11,800 --> 01:13:15,031
<i>which would've meant</i>
<i>my spending some time in Europe.</i>

897
