901
01:13:42,560 --> 01:13:45,632
I... I've something to tell you both.

902
01:13:45,760 --> 01:13:48,354
<i>We're heading for</i>
<i>the best pirate days ever.</i>

903
01:13:48,480 --> 01:13:50,789
I...

904
01:13:54,440 --> 01:14:00,709
It looks as if... as though Mummy
and I are going to have to split up,

